<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style=3D"text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Instructions to the =
NSO participants</strong></span><strong>:</strong></p>
<p><strong><br>
</strong></p>
<p>1.&nbsp;&nbsp; They should attend the selection with proper sportswear. =
(Other dress <strong>
i.e. Shirt, Pant,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=3D"font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;&n=
bsp;</strong><strong style=3D"font-size: 12pt;">Bermuda&#8217;s etc. is not=
 allowed</strong><span style=3D"font-size: 12pt;">).</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"font-size: 12pt;"><br>
</span></p>
<p>2.&nbsp;&nbsp; Do not bring valuable things (i.e. Cell phone, Gold ornam=
ents, Cash, Debit / ATM card etc.)<br>
</p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p>3.&nbsp;&nbsp; The selection results will be announced on the same day a=
s soon as the programme is over.<br>
</p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p>4.&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>A student can participate in as many sports he / =
she wants and give his / her preference. However, final</strong><strong>&nb=
sp;</strong><strong style=3D"font-size: 12pt;">decision will be taken by th=
e NSO committee.</strong></p>
<p><strong style=3D"font-size: 12pt;"><br>
</strong></p>
<p>5.&nbsp;&nbsp; The NSO selection of results will be displayed on all the=
 Hostel notice board (tentatively).<br>
</p>
<p><br>
</p>
<p>6.&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Medically unfit students are not eligible </stron=
g>to undergo NSO programme.
</p>
